        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="1073" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1073">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 (Potsdam)/7–2045</note>
                <head>No. 1073<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Proposal by the Soviet Delegation</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content" calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-20">July 20, 1945</date>
                </dateline>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation—Extract<note n="1" xml:id="d1073fn1">For
                            the other portions of this proposal, see <ref target="#d804">documents
                                Nos. 804</ref> and <ref target="#d1064">1064</ref>.</note>]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The Yalta Declaration “On Liberated Europe”</hi>
                </p>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Russian Proposal Presented to Foreign Ministers, July</hi>
                    20, 1945<note n="2" xml:id="d1073fn2">See <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_150">p. 150</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <p>… Moreover, the present Greek Government is breaking the peace with their
                    neighbors and threatening Albania and Bulgaria with military action. All those
                    circumstances create the necessity of taking urgent measures to eliminate such a
                    situation in Greece.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
            </div>
        </body>
